WEBVTT

00:06:29.368 --> 00:06:31.633
and try to imagine
everything that can happen.

00:06:31.657 --> 00:06:36.528
I need to deal with thousands
and thousands of variables,

00:06:36.552 --> 00:06:38.747
conditions and possibilities.

00:06:38.771 --> 00:06:42.884
As a consequence, where a film script
is about 100 pages,

00:06:43.969 --> 00:06:50.003
an interactive script like this
is between four and five thousand pages.

00:06:51.319 --> 00:06:55.485
So that gives you an idea
of what this work is about.

00:06:55.509 --> 00:07:00.940
But I think, in the end,
the experience is very unique,